	<text>Contents</text>
</context>
<context>
	<score>0.4665032</score>
	<text>The Council of Europe body ECRI alleged in its Third report on Bulgaria of June 2003 that Roma encounter &quot;serious difficulties in many spheres of life&quot;, elaborating that:</text>
</context>
<context>
	<score>0.46300185</score>
	<text>Noted Roma from Bulgaria include musicians Azis , Sofi Marinova and Ivo Papazov , surgeon Aleksandar Chirkov, politician Toma Tomov, footballer Marian Ognyanov , 1988 Olympic boxing champion Ismail Mustafov.</text>
